<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>密码重置 - Gatrix</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a202c 0%, #2d3748 50%, #4a5568 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d3748 0%, #4a5568 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .header p {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: rgba(45, 55, 72, 0.8);
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #f7fafc;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #cbd5e0;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
    }
    .security-notice {
      background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
    }
    .security-notice p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #a0aec0;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      background: rgba(26, 32, 44, 0.8);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .footer p {
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container { margin: 20px; }
      .header, .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🔐 密码重置</h1>
      <p>Gatrix 账户安全</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>您好！👋</h2>
      <p>我们收到了重置您 Gatrix 账户密码的请求。</p>
      <p>请点击下面的按钮安全地设置您的新密码：</p>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">🔑 设置新密码</a>
      </div>

      <div class="security-notice">
        <p><strong>⏰ 重要提醒：</strong> 为了您的安全，此链接将在1小时后自动过期。</p>
      </div>

      <p>如果您没有请求密码重置，可以安全地忽略此邮件。您的账户仍然安全。</p>

      <p>如有任何疑问，请随时联系我们的客服团队。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2025 Gatrix. 保留所有权利。</p>
      <p>此邮件为自动发送，请勿回复。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
